query: SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS character_name, MIN(mi_idx.info) AS rating, MIN(n.name) AS playing_actor, MIN(t.title) AS complete_hero_movie FROM complete_cast AS cc, comp_cast_type AS cct1, comp_cast_type AS cct2, char_name AS chn, cast_info AS ci, info_type AS it2, keyword AS k, kind_type AS kt, movie_info_idx AS mi_idx, movie_keyword AS mk, name AS n, title AS t WHERE kt.id = t.kind_id AND t.id = mk.movie_id AND t.id = ci.movie_id AND t.id = cc.movie_id AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = ci.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND cc.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id AND n.id = ci.person_id AND k.id = mk.keyword_id AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id AND cct2.id = cc.status_id AND it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id AND chn.name not like '%Wonder Woman%' AND chn.name not like '%Groot%' AND chn.name not like '%Neo%' AND chn.name not like '%R2-D2%' AND cct1.kind in ('complete+verified','complete','crew') AND cct2.kind not in ('complete+verified','complete','crew') AND t.production_year > 1994 AND t.production_year < 2012 AND it2.info not in ('LD contrast','magazine cover photo','crazy credits','books','languages','LD sound encoding','LD analog right','LD audio quality','LD certification','LD label','LD video quality','other works','LD disc format','LD close captions-teletext-ld-g','printed media reviews','LD number','LD frequency response','LD dialogue intellegibility','birth date','LD release date') AND k.keyword not like '%rebellion%' AND k.keyword not like '%rescue%' AND (n.name like '%Q%') AND n.gender in ('f')
